                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A carrion dreg gains additional abilities based on the body parts it has scavenged. Roll 1d6 and consult the table below to add one of these abilities randomly, or pick one. <table class=\"inner\"> <tr> <td><b>d6</b></td> <td><b>Ability</b></td> </tr> <tr> <td>1</td> <td>Grasping Arms: The carrion dreg gains a climb speed of 20 feet.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>2</td> <td>Leathery Wings: The carrion dreg gains an extraordinary fly speed of 20 feet with clumsy maneuverability.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>3</td> <td>Rotting Fins: The carrion dreg gains a swim speed of 30 feet.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>4</td> <td>Rough Hide: The carrion dreg gains a +1 bonus to its KAC.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>5</td> <td>Sharp Fangs: The carrion dreg\u2019s bite attack deals an additional amount of damage equal to half the dreg\u2019s Strength modifier.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>6</td> <td>Solid Thews: The carrion dreg gains 10% additional Hit Points.</td> </tr> </table>",
